her engagement with the revolution

00:29:26.790 --> 00:29:29.860
for the first time in public,
and for the last time in private,

00:29:29.860 --> 00:29:32.700
the to team that Bustamante
gathered in their quest

00:29:32.700 --> 00:29:34.000
to meet the last living Soldadera.

00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:35.500
