withstood the chiding of others,

00:30:07.740 --> 00:30:11.250
as she demanded her revolutionary
pension and I quote, "Vocally,

00:30:11.250 --> 00:30:13.580
insisting that she had bled,
fought, and mothered children

00:30:13.580 --> 00:30:15.040
